data.description: Welcome to 4757 Sheffield. When you arrive, you will see the expansive, screened-in porch which contains two large sheds for additional storage. You then enter the large living room with gleaming hardwood floors and ample natural lighting throughout. The Kitchen features upgraded granite countertops, ceramic flooring, stainless steel appliances and gas cooking. There is a separate Formal Dining Room with hardwood floors as well. Upstairs you will find 3 bedrooms with hardwood flooring and a Full Bath with ceramic tile flooring. The Primary Bedroom features two spacious closets. The other two bedrooms are a nice size with single closets. The Finished, Daylight Basement has been expanded and features ceramic flooring. Off the kitchen you walk out to your private deck with outside kitchen for dining and entertaining. The Full Bath has all new fixtures. The electrical service coming into the house has been updated - all new. This home is very close to major travel routes including I-95 and within walking distance to area shopping and dining.
